Description:
Dutch Agency for decorative, architectural, office, hospitality and retail-lighting, founded in 2017. 

Brands represented are;
Linea Light Group (architectural, professional, Italy), Stilnovo (design, Italy), Lightnet (architectural, Germany), Diomede (outdoor, Italy), Lightpoint (design, Denmark), B.Lux (architectural/design, Spain), Frandsen (design, Denmark)

HANDSOME is a professional Electronic and Industrial Automation Connectors and Cables Harness Solutions supplier. The company has strong technical strength, adheres to the concept of high-quality customer service, and always serves the electrical safety connection industry.

The Main Products are: 

Serial Cable;
Machine Vision Cables;
Sensor Cables;
Serve Motor Cables;
PLC Cables;
Industrial Robot Cables;
Connectors.
And many other connectors and cables harness supplies. 

In order to further meet the needs of users, HANDSOME also customizes the Connectors and Cables for your industrial automation facilities and equipment for customers.

Contact Me, Sales@handsomecable.com
Website: Https://handsomecable.com
Store: Https://handsomesales.com

Fundada em 1997, e empresa integrante do Grupo TESTA, a Prome, antes designada Macorlux, é a empresa lider de mercado nacional no sector do comércio por grosso de elecrodoméstico. 

Somos uma empresa, em contínua expansão, assente em valores comerciais e éticos que nos colocam num elevado patamar de qualidade, competitividade, inovação e profissionalismo.

O que nos diferencia?

- Líderes de mercado na distribuição de electrodomésticos;
- Maior centro logístico de distribuição de electrodomésticos
em Portugal (17.000m2);
- Mais de 10.000 referências de produtos em stock permanente;
- Representantes das marcas mais conceituadas do mercado;
- Acesso a profissionais em plataforma online (B2B);
- Integração “API” para clientes com páginas online;
- Apoio e acompanhamento profissional empresas.

"ACCUTRADE POLSKA" Sp. z o.o.  – to firma należąca do międzynarodowej grupy dystrybucyjnej kierującej swoją ofertę przede wszystkim do sektora MOTIVE POWER.

W Polsce jesteśmy oficjalnym dystrybutorem marek akumulatorów SIAP, ROLLS, CHALLNEGER oraz ładowarek S.P.E Elettronica, T.C.E. Group.

Accutrade - to:

    wieloletnie doświadczenie w pracy z akumulatorami zasilającymi trakcyjnymi i semi-trakcyjnymi;

    zespół specjalistów dla których każde zadanie to wyzwanie i przygoda;

    doradztwo w zakresie doboru akumulatora i wsparcie techniczne.

    duży wybór akumulatorów dostępnych w magazynie;

    ceny od bezpośredniego dostawcy;

    obsługa gwarancyjna i serwisowa;

    usługa regeneracji akumulatorów wszystkich marek

